962ca6f620726549211703144bd5aa130e490","tid":1190454,"uid":127929,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:20:25.000Z","msg":"完全封鎖「巴奥&bull;薩基路加」後將隱藏所有該會員的主題、回覆及被引用回覆。如日後需解除封鎖，請於「帳號」內的「封鎖會員」中設定。"},{"pid":"82ed591eb5229ea3f1b39a03eed56d819e51326f","tid":1190454,"uid":61398,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:25:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a58e677b5ec2cb4c70b16262250b5f4cb16b9cd8","tid":1190454,"uid":53498,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:25:20.000Z","msg":"通過咗,第時行行下街畀支共落孖葉拉去支那坐監,仲驚乜無咗份工？"},{"pid":"fa648b18a829f1a7e5a14b0cc3e5431ef8147f34","tid":1190454,"uid":12149,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">( Show Blocked User - 巴奥&bull;薩基路加 )</span>"},{"pid":"6ea83fd2c6700879420a4eaea09e0e0f4fa4f4ee","tid":1190454,"uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事關香港歷史之重大變局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想借大家少少位用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家可以原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n共匪以分化起家，一開始1920年代就已經搞到國民黨分裂，後來更加以分化打敗國民政府奪得大權，而今次呢招自己人扮打自己人再嫁禍比對家，喺人類歴史上已經沿用多年，所以如果話呢件事99%機會一係警察/ 一係請爛仔自編自導（參考《十年》），打撃對家士氣甚至互相指責，削弱示威力量，係言之常情，總之搞到你反共勢力嘅內亂，就係三毛最想樂見嘅現象<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOPvJL6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOPvJL6.png&h=344452d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻止惡法！為時未晚！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意返由於預計示威人數好多，民陣已經將起點改咗喺維園！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n<br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n<br />\n集合地點：<span style=\"color: red;\">銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）</span><br />\n<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n百國聯軍助陣！感謝海外港人為香港人嘅未來而作出嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AG0SmhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAG0SmhW.png&h=5d5fe630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n好重要所以要講三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8ugzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=d04753ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（全球聯署、白宮聯署、學界、各行各業、宗教、地區/ 海外港人等等）反送中聯署合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY%2Fhtmlview&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8ugzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=25289fcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>愛因斯坦 (Albert Einstein)：「The world will not be destoryed by those who do evil, but by these who watch them without doing anything.(這個世界不會被那些作惡多端的人毀滅，而是冷眼旁觀、選擇保持緘默的人)」；鄭有傑(導演):「良心的沉默是邪惡的幫兇。」<br />\n<br />\n好多時歷史中嘅轉折位都係由表面上微不足道嘅小事/小人物而形成嘅，所以我地更加唔可以睇小自己</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7346f67f97c7dd5a71c9c3e3ec60f24fe113a827","tid":1190454,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"82ed591eb5229ea3f1b39a03eed56d819e51326f","tid":1190454,"uid":61398,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e8ce7f755977a92924a4119cc5e659ab9de6a29e","tid":1190454,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"可能會俾人點相，分分鐘之後連份工都冇咩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能會有暴力衝突，差佬分分鐘亂咁捉人，甚至開槍連命都冇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請補充！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:25:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:28:15.000Z","msg":"我一直支持和平理性非暴力唔講粗口散步式表達意見，但怕有內鬼，天氣熱怕後生仔火爆跟住衝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3531219530a52f12b18590e0f823ebfe37a89d0b","tid":1190454,"uid":188125,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"「五毛大V」袁小靚丈夫被北京拘押 向澳媒哭求澳洲出手救夫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1106006\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1106006</a><br />\n<br />\n中国人郭紹傑：不明白被捕原因 律師：罪成最高刑罰監禁3年<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1135486\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1135486</a><br />\n<br />\n前車可鑑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f803e8eb061ef39a27170b4ec227bef0